#. Id: 55153-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 0.0
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#. -- Condition: In town(s) of faction(s): Ancient Ruins or Second Empire or The Old Empire
#: 55153-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Hoy, what I need is a good hard drink..."
msgstr "好，我需要的是一杯好喝的..."

#. Id: 55154-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (55153-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#. Id: 55171-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (55169-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55154-Dialogue.mod:0 55171-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Did you want somethi-"
msgstr "你想要什麼嗎？"

#. Id: 55158-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 2.0
#. -- Parent line: 1 (55154-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55158-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "My partner, /NAME/ stabbed me in the back, see. Took the loot after we set up camp, disappeared by the morning. Know what betrayal feels like? Like being hit in the back of the skull with a rusty club. Literally, in my case..."
msgstr ""

#. Id: 55159-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (55158-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55159-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "I'm sorry to hear that..."
msgstr "聽到這個消息我很遺憾"

#. Id: 55161-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (55159-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: NUM_BACKPACKS>0, Tag: -1
#: 55161-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Anyway, judging by that hefty bag of yours, I'm guessing you've had plenty of luck tech hunting, am I right?"
msgstr "無論如何，從你那個沉重的包來判斷，我猜你有很多運氣科技狩獵，我是對的嗎？"

#. Id: 55161-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.1
#. -- Parent line: 3 (55159-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#. -- Condition: Who: TARGET, Condition: NUM_BACKPACKS>0, Tag: -1
#: 55161-Dialogue.mod:1
msgid "Anyway, looks like you're carrying a heavy load in that bag of yours. Here's hoping you've had more luck than me with your tech hunting..."
msgstr "無論如何，看起來你在你的那個包裡承受著沉重的負擔。這里希望你的技術狩獵比我更幸運..."

#. Id: 55162-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (55159-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55162-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "How about you? Had any luck hunting? You know, Skeletech, that's the good stuff, I consider myself a collector of sorts... Found any?"
msgstr "你呢？有運氣狩獵嗎？你知道，Skeletech，這是好東西，我認為自己是各種各樣的收藏家......找到了嗎？"

#. Id: 55162-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.1
#. -- Parent line: 3 (55159-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55162-Dialogue.mod:1
msgid "How about you anyway, /OUTLANDER/? Found any decent loot? Tell me you've had better luck than me..."
msgstr ""

#. Id: 55162-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.2
#. -- Parent line: 3 (55159-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55162-Dialogue.mod:2
msgid "What about you? Found anything interesting? Artifacts, Skeletech, super weapons...? Save my morale here, /OUTLANDER/, I was just starting to lose hope..."
msgstr ""

#. Id: 55162-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.3
#. -- Parent line: 3 (55159-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55162-Dialogue.mod:3
msgid "How about you, find anything? Gotta show your findings to your fellow adventurers, you know... Tech hunter code... [They nod proudly to themselves]"
msgstr "你怎麼樣，找到什麼？要向你的冒險家們展示你的發現，你知道......技術獵人代碼...... [他們自豪地向自己點頭]"

#. Id: 55163-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (55162-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55163-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "/IWE/'ve found a few bits and pieces."
msgstr ""

#. Id: 55163-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.1
#. -- Parent line: 4 (55162-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55163-Dialogue.mod:1
msgid "Of course. You're looking at a master adventurer."
msgstr "當然。你正在尋找一位冒險家。"

#. Id: 55164-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 6.0
#. -- Parent line: 5 (55163-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#. -- Condition: Who: ME, Condition: PERSONALITY_TAG=0, Tag: TRAITOROUS
#. -- Condition: Who: ME, Condition: PERSONALITY_TAG=0, Tag: BRAVE
#. -- Condition: Who: ME, Condition: PERSONALITY_TAG=0, Tag: MANIACAL
#: 55164-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Marvellous... Look, how about we join forces a while? Might be a thing or two for me to learn from a pro like yourself, eh?"
msgstr "奇妙......看，我們一起加入力量怎麼樣？對我來說，向像我這樣的職業選手學習可能是一兩件事，嗯？"

#. Id: 55164-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 6.1
#. -- Parent line: 5 (55163-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#. -- Condition: Who: ME, Condition: PERSONALITY_TAG=0, Tag: TRAITOROUS
#. -- Condition: Who: ME, Condition: PERSONALITY_TAG=0, Tag: BRAVE
#. -- Condition: Who: ME, Condition: PERSONALITY_TAG=0, Tag: MANIACAL
#: 55164-Dialogue.mod:1
msgid "Great stuff, /BROTHER/, I sure could use a partner like you. How about we work together, split the loot between us?"
msgstr ""

#. Id: 55176-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 7.0
#. -- Parent line: 6 (55164-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55176-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "All you tech hunters are the same, you're only after my loot!"
msgstr "所有技術獵人都是一樣的，你只是在我的戰利品之後！"

#. Id: 55181-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 8.0
#. -- Parent line: 7 (55176-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55181-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "I... just wanted some company..."
msgstr "我...只想要一些公司......"

#. Id: 55177-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 7.0
#. -- Parent line: 6 (55164-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55177-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Sorry, no room for rookies."
msgstr "對不起，沒有新手的空間。"

#. Id: 55182-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 8.0
#. -- Parent line: 7 (55177-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55182-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "I'll show you whose a rookie! Just you wait, I'll find the mother lode of Skeletech and you'll regret ever rejecting me!"
msgstr "我會告訴你誰是新秀！等你，我會找到Skeletech的母親，你會後悔拒絕我！"

#. Id: 55178-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 7.0
#. -- Parent line: 6 (55164-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55178-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Why not? Could use some extra muscle..."
msgstr "為什麼不？可以使用一些額外的肌肉......"

#. Id: 55186-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 8.0
#. -- Parent line: 7 (55178-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55186-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Then let's go get rich!"
msgstr "然後讓我們變得富有！"

#. Id: 55179-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 9.0
#. -- Parent line: 8 (55186-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55179-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Good to have some company on the road, /BROTHER/..."
msgstr ""

#. Id: 55165-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 6.0
#. -- Parent line: 5 (55163-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55165-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Well, then I guess it looks like my luck's finally turned, eh? This time round, my treasure's walked right into my hands!"
msgstr "嗯，那我覺得好像我的運氣終於轉了，是嗎？這一次，我的寶貝一直走到我的手中！"

#. Id: 55166-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 7.0
#. -- Parent line: 6 (55165-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55166-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Hand over the loot!"
msgstr "交出戰利品！"

#. Id: 55173-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (55162-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55173-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Don't think that's any of your business."
msgstr "不要以為這是你的任何業務。"

#. Id: 55187-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 6.0
#. -- Parent line: 5 (55173-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55187-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "... Hoggin' all the loot and you won't even share, eh? What kinda attitude is that amongst your fellow tech hunters?"
msgstr "...... Hoggin'所有的戰利品，你甚至不會分享，是嗎？在你的科技獵手中，你有什麼樣的態度？"

#. Id: 55188-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 7.0
#. -- Parent line: 6 (55187-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55188-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "See, stranger, I don't like competition. And out here in these ruins, there ain't no-one around but the dead ancients to hear you scream..."
msgstr "看，陌生人，我不喜歡比賽。在這些廢墟中，周圍沒有人，但死去的古人聽到你尖叫......"

#. Id: 55189-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 8.0
#. -- Parent line: 7 (55188-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#. Id: 55111-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (55101-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter Rival
#: 55189-Dialogue.mod:0 55111-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "A rival tech hunter is a dead tech hunter!"
msgstr "對手技術獵人是一個死技術獵人！"

#. Id: 55174-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (55162-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55174-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Nope, no luck."
msgstr "不，沒有運氣。"

#. Id: 55202-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 6.0
#. -- Parent line: 5 (55174-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55202-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Ain't that a shame. Looks like we'll both be heading back home with our tails between our legs, eh..."
msgstr "這不是一個恥辱。看起來我們兩個都會在我們的雙腿之間走回家，呃......"

#. Id: 55213-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 7.0
#. -- Parent line: 6 (55202-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55213-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Safe travels, /OUTLANDER/"
msgstr ""

#. Id: 55199-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (55162-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55199-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "You've mistaken me. I'm no adventurer."
msgstr "你誤會了我。我不是冒險家。"

#. Id: 55200-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 6.0
#. -- Parent line: 5 (55199-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55200-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Huh. Strange place to hang out if you're not adventuring. Nothing but bones and relics around these parts."
msgstr "呵呵。如果你沒有冒險，那就是閒逛的奇怪地方。除了這些部分周圍的骨頭和遺物外什麼都沒有。"

#. Id: 55201-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 7.0
#. -- Parent line: 6 (55200-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55201-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Safe travels anyway, /OUTLANDER/"
msgstr ""

#. Id: 55198-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (55160-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55198-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Kch... No sense of comradery these days..."
msgstr "Kch ......這些天沒有同志的感覺......"

#. Id: 55198-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.1
#. -- Parent line: 3 (55160-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55198-Dialogue.mod:1
msgid "Tch... No sense of brotherhood these days..."
msgstr "Tch ......這些天沒有兄弟情誼......"

#. Id: 55172-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (55158-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55172-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Shit happens."
msgstr "屎發生了。"

#. Id: 55155-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (55153-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#. Id: 55193-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (55169-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55155-Dialogue.mod:0 55193-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "That's too bad but-"
msgstr "那太糟糕但是 - "

#. Id: 55156-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (55153-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#. Id: 55195-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (55169-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55156-Dialogue.mod:0 55195-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Sounds rough..."
msgstr "聽起來很粗糙......"

#. Id: 55168-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 0.0
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#. -- Condition: In town(s) of faction(s): Ancient Ruins
#: 55168-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Hoo, it's been a long week! [They sip on a flask of drink] ... Wanna swig? "
msgstr "嘿，這是一個漫長的一周！ [他們啜飲一瓶飲料] ...想喝酒嗎？"

#. Id: 55170-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (55168-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55170-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Sure, why no-"
msgstr "當然，為什麼不 - "

#. Id: 55152-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 2.0
#. -- Parent line: 1 (55170-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55152-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "First I get chased so far by a swarm of bugs that my lungs near exploded. Then, I lose my partner, /NAME/, in the ruins. Which, might I add, were a sweet waste of all effort! Damn concrete graveyard was emptied long before I got there..."
msgstr ""

#. Id: 55192-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (55168-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55192-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "No thanks, I-"
msgstr "不，謝謝，我 - "

#. Id: 55194-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (55168-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55194-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "What is-"
msgstr "什麼是-"

#. Id: 55169-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 0.0
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#. -- Condition: In town(s) of faction(s): Ancient Ruins or Second Empire or The Old Empire
#: 55169-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Tell me you've had better luck than me here, stranger... Because I've had one hell of a week..."
msgstr "告訴我你在這裡比我好運，陌生人......因為我有一個星期的地獄......"

#. Id: 55157-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 2.0
#. -- Parent line: 1 (55171-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Tech Hunter talk to
#: 55157-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Took me three weeks to travel to these ruins. Get here and nothin'. Nada. Place's been completely ransacked already. Hoy, the lady's gonna wring my neck when I go back empty handed..."
msgstr "我花了三個星期去了這些廢墟。來到這裡，沒什麼。納達。地方已被徹底洗劫一空。好的，當我空手而歸的時候，這位女士要擰我的脖子......"
